---
title: Smart Cheddar Beef Patties with Maple-BBQ Sauce and Fresh Salad
description: These flavours will leave your tastebuds begging for more! Savoury beef patties are basted in maple-BBQ sauce and topped with sharp cheddar. A fresh salad with crunchy apples makes this meal both delicious and nutritious!

